":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:41:29.000Z","msg":"點解唔光復多次上水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:25:55.000Z","msg":"上水試過好多次 冇一次work 唔好搞住"},{"pid":"245ac76bdb4a04091657213ef6ee1e9ef98b62bc","tid":1289790,"uid":96945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:26:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d4b739c731c32f6f60f3f34fb98ab46d4cd35ddb","tid":1289790,"uid":271251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:39:56.000Z","msg":"sudan今日都抗爭成功,大家要一齊加油!!"},{"pid":"35ea9c0ff3c2b7faa2cefd8cf685ae276a9fde34","tid":1289790,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c9792fc4667f0dcf9bc1a7579b4ddbe804efc17","tid":1289790,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T08:57:00.000Z","msg":"confirm 行程：<br />\n7-7 尖沙咀 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1285728\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1285728</a><br />\n暫定行程：<br />\n7-14 沙田 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1287850\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1287850</a><br />\n7-21 大埔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1288561\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1288561</a><br />\n<br />\n和理非遊行目的好簡單，就係示威，要政府回應五大訴求：<br />\n1. 撤底撤回逃犯條例修訂<br />\n2. 撤銷所有「暴動」定義<br />\n3. 釋放受反送中有關事件被捕人士<br />\n4. 成立獨立委員會調查警隊暴力<br />\n5. 實行立法會及行政長官雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n無論民陣定民間自發，總之政府一日未正面回應五大訴求，一日都唔可以俾呢團火熄。你覺得遊行冇用，係因為每次行完政府唔理你你就算數。<br />\n<br />\n請大家要持之以恆，韓國人反樸槿惠示威，每星期六都行，行左三個月，行到總統下台；德國人週一示威，每星期一放工就出黎行，行左半年，行到東德有真普選，過多半年柏林圍牆倒下。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道香港人每周日出黎行，最終會帶黎乜野改變，但係我唔想我地香港人，連做都未做過，就因為政府唔理而接受左！！！！<br />\n<br />\n其實每周日和理非遊行，只不過係好基本既理性抗爭，既唔危險亦冇風險，歡迎一家大細參加，當做公民教育又好乜都好，請將你每周日既family day，變成family walk，飲完茶就出黎散下步，幫助消化。<br />\n<br />\n最後，好多人話搞18區遊行，一星期一區，我覺得係好事，但唔希望俾「地區」呢個概念騎劫。一掛上地區牌頭，好多唔係果區既人就唔會理，反送中同真普選係全香港既事，18區遊行，每一次都係反送中大遊行，714沙田遊行唔係沙田人既遊行，係「第五次全港反送中遊行」，係全港人都應該參加既遊行。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:45:32.000Z","msg":"講得啱<br />\n遊行名稱唔洗加上地區名更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b6ebbd425bea99b5c760666fa40089954c66b9b","tid":1289790,"uid":188708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:49:07.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\nMust Support"},{"pid":"f31dd55499faa51f5ed6a39557a96881123c7cd6","tid":1289790,"uid":44174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:50:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c68826a47acd1375581c62659952fdde21d561fb","tid":1289790,"uid":260201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:50:46.000Z","msg":"冇野講呀冇野講"},{"pid":"f70af677ffbe1b9e07bba213274ddb015a0d0d27","tid":1289790,"uid":274569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7921852ccc4b94396fe98be491b2f64a6454f9e2","tid":1289790,"uid":261556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:12:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"123a98fe2ce4ad882f4a48a2689547feef30028e","tid":1289790,"uid":50890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:27:48.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"78e897d02f0046bf4a3bdef7b3f33111a0f4e65e","tid":1289790,"uid":25787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:31:05.000Z","msg":"推，支持"},{"pid":"9dda6750222e8a5cd2da53cf9860ff3105948812","tid":1289790,"uid":258910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T18:03:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"319f1bf4c5fecce1ed42bc38f7984f1c4f1619ec","tid":1289790,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20b37530e46805415ac805baf4b47792c678a51d","tid":1289790,"uid":82947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3e751a006c779d929cd81ce171cb27c4c9dacc1","tid":1289790,"uid":52817,"like":143,"dislike":2,"score":141,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T11:54:02.000Z","msg":"update 714沙田已獲不反對通知書"},"citedBy